data.description: This Keizer house is ready for you to make it your home! 3 bd 2.5 baths near shopping and schools. HVAC updated 2018. SS appliances 2018. Main floor room can be a den, office, bdrm or use your imagination. Fully fenced backyard with amazing space for entertaining.  Primary suite has large walk in closet and bathroom. **Assumable VA Loan**
